.TH PRODBOX_config 1
.SH NAME
prodbox-config \- Configuration management
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B prodbox config
.SH DESCRIPTION
Repository-root Dhall configuration commands.
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
\fBsetup\fR
Interactively author config
.TP
\fBshow\fR
Display current config
.TP
\fBvalidate\fR
Validate current config
.TP
\fBschema\fR
Regenerate Dhall schema files
.TP
\fBgenerate\fR
Generate the default non-secret config
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
\fBprodbox config validate\fR
Validate the config before running lifecycle commands.
